IO-Socket-ByteCounter version 0.0.2
==================================

See POD for documentation:

   perldoc IO::Socket::ByteCounter;

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl -MCPAN -e 'install IO::Socket::ByteCounter;'

or

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


